And these people came with, I mean, what is clearly falsehood.

225
00:21:05,913 --> 00:21:08,380
They came with things fixed in their mind.

226
00:21:08,380 --> 00:21:13,044
They say "you counted the letter in this way, but they should be counted in another way,"

227
00:21:13,044 --> 00:21:14,608
which is a wrong way.

228
00:21:14,608 --> 00:21:21,368
However, when I presented the paper, I gave them numbers, not even letters.

229
00:21:21,368 --> 00:21:27,691
They can take the letters, but they should have changed their minds then, because there's no argument against the numbers.

230
00:21:27,691 --> 00:21:31,574
If you take all the numbers in the Quran and add them up, you have a multiple of 19.

231
00:21:31,574 --> 00:21:34,550
This has nothing to do with letters.

232
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:40,919
But God says the reason they insisted on going to hell,

233
00:21:40,919 --> 00:21:45,909
and the reason they're subjected to that terrible retribution which is not enough for them,

234
00:21:45,909 --> 00:21:50,319
is because we have given them the truth, but they hated the truth.

235
00:21:54,428 --> 00:21:55,857
Aqem Al-Salat.